              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Slow Beam-Pulsing System was Used to Provide",
                "Activation Periods of 0.5 Sec Followed by 4 Sec",
                "Measuring Intervals.  Slowly Decaying Activities were",
                "Investigated with Correspondingly Longer Measuring",
                "Periods."
              ]
            }
          ],
